name: Restore thumbnails and expando buttons on reddit.
description: Admins did rush a css change without proper testing and frankly horrid looks. This reverts that change.
css:
@-moz-document domain("www.reddit.com") {
html body .content .expando-button.selftext.collapsed, 
html body .content .expando-button.selftext.collapsed:hover,
html body .content .eb-sch,
html body .content .expando-button.selftext.expanded,
html body .content .eb-se,
html body .content .expando-button.selftext.expanded:hover,
html body .content .eb-seh,
html body .content .expando-button.video.collapsed,
html body .content .expando-button.video.collapsed:hover,
html body .content .eb-vch,
html body .content .expando-button.video.expanded,
html body .content .eb-ve,
html body .content .expando-button.video.expanded:hover,
html body .content .eb-veh,
html body .content .thumbnail.nsfw,
html body .content .thumbnail.self,
html body .content .thumbnail.image,
html body .content .thumbnail.default
{
    background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,');
}

html body .content .expando-button {
    height: 23px;
    width: 23px;
    margin: 2px 5px 2px 0;
    background-color: #fff;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-attachment: scroll;
}

html body .content .expando-button.selftext.collapsed {
    background-position: 0 -584px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}

html body .content .expando-button.selftext.collapsed:hover,
html body .content .eb-sch {
    background-position: -92px -547px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}

html body .content .expando-button.selftext.expanded,
html body .content .eb-se {
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    background-position: -58px -584px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}

html body .content .expando-button.selftext.expanded:hover,
html body .content .eb-seh {
    background-position: -29px -584px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}

html body .content .expando-button.video.collapsed {
    background-position: 0 -613px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}

html body .content .expando-button.video.collapsed:hover,
html body .content .eb-vch {
    background-position: -87px -584px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}

html body .content .expando-button.video.expanded,
html body .content .eb-ve {
    background-position: -58px -613px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}

html body .content .expando-button.video.expanded:hover,
html body .content .eb-veh {
    background-position: -29px -613px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}


html body .content .thumbnail {
    float: left;
    font-size: 0;
    margin: 0;
    margin-right: 5px;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
    width: 70px;
}

html body .content .thumbnail.nsfw {
    height: 70px;
    background-position: 0 -359px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}

html body .content .thumbnail.self {
    height: 50px;
    background-position: 0 -491px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}

html body .content .thumbnail.default {
    height: 50px;
    background-position: 0 -435px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}




}
